{"tid":1450270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:58:19.000Z","uid":56602,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b709a021facbf0946089f57df1cedde6e6214120","tid":1450270,"uid":56602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:27:58.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=4b1ebbba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=902556f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"9ba7afb283ff095c93988d2137cdbf4bce788caa","tid":1450270,"uid":135334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n黑警還眼"},{"pid":"5b613ba1af65efda14a186d0d2d87626e534c83e","tid":1450270,"uid":258297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"205dd3f0fb6e1b6e09f6509c601c4f551703cb82","tid":1450270,"uid":103527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRuxEEz.jpg\" dat